Package: homeBudget
Type: Package
Title: Maintain records and report on spending, income, and savings
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Rafael", "Kuttner", email = "r.i.kuttner@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <r.i.kuttner@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/rkuttner7/homeBudget
BugReports: https://github.com/rkuttner7/homeBudget/issues
Description: Keep a record of all spending, including both credit
    cards and checks, as well as income from salaries, 
    interest, and investments. Report on categories of spending
    and relative balance to earnings. Also, check for irregular
    values such as fraud or incorrect monthly billing totals.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
